Privacy Policy for Encrypted
Introduction
Encrypted respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use the Bot. Please read this policy carefully. If you do not agree with the terms of this privacy policy, please do not use the Bot.

Information We Collect
1. User-Provided Information
Messages and Content: We collect and store the messages and content you submit through the Bot, including any personal information contained within those messages.
User IDs: We may collect your Discord user ID, server ID, and other relevant identifiers.
2. Automatically Collected Information
Usage Data: We collect information about your interactions with the Bot, such as the commands you use and the responses provided by the Bot.
Log Data: We may log information when you access the Bot, including your IP address, browser type, and access times.
How We Use Your Information
3. To Provide and Improve Our Services
Functionality: To enable the Bot to function as intended and provide you with its features and services.
Improvements: To understand and analyze usage patterns and improve the Bot’s functionality and user experience.
4. To Communicate with You
Support: To respond to your inquiries, provide customer support, and send updates and information related to the Bot.
Sharing Your Information
5. Third-Party Services
Service Providers: We may share your information with third-party service providers who perform services on our behalf, such as hosting and data analysis.
Legal Requirements: We may disclose your information if required to do so by law or in response to valid requests by public authorities.
6. Data Security
We use reasonable administrative, technical, and physical measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, use, modification, or disclosure. However, no method of transmission over the internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure.
Your Rights and Choices
7. Access and Control
Access: You have the right to access the personal data we hold about you and to request corrections if necessary.
Deletion: You can request that we delete your personal data, subject to certain exceptions.
8. Data Retention
We retain your personal data only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy, unless a longer retention period is required or permitted by law.
Children’s Privacy
9. Children’s Information
The Bot is not intended for use by children under the age of 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal data from children under 13. If we become aware that we have collected personal data from a child under 13, we will take steps to delete such information.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
10. Updates
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. Your continued use of the Bot after any changes constitutes your acceptance of the new Privacy Policy.
Contact Us
11. Contact Information
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at support@wolfstudios.xyz.
